reading function for the Burgers vector\ndensity. As a consequence, the Burgers vector density spreads differently in\ndifferent crystal structures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Jun 2017 19:36:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Oct 2017 18:35:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-26"}
